# Docs ↔ Code Sync

Docs and code must describe the same behavior.

- When docs change, update code in the same task (or fix docs if they were wrong).
- When code changes user-visible behavior or public APIs, update the docs.
- Final check: someone reading only the docs or only the code must get the correct picture.